here\'s a little bit,\" the old woman replied.Then beady said:“How do I do a chance?”\nOver time, the queen had a beautiful boy.&page&The king was not hunting, so the witch (the first stepmother was originally a witch) came to the room where the queen was lying down.\n“Now, the bath is ready.The bath will be good for your body and encourage new vitality.Please hurry up before the water is called. ”&page&The daughter (the daughter of the witch) was also next to it.\nThus, they (witches and daughters) took the fragile queen into the bath, put them in her bathtub, closed the door and ran away.&page&The beautiful young queen eventually died because they made the stove in the bathroom as crazy.\nWhen this worked, the witch put her daughter on her daughter (her hat) and lying in her bed instead of her queen.&page&The witch gave his daughter a queen\'s body and face, but he couldn\'t give one eye that had not been one of the original things.\nBut it was lying down so that the king could not see his face.&page&In the evening, the king returned to the palace and heard that the queen gave birth to his son, and he was really happy to see the state of his wife.It is.The queen should not yet see the light.I need to rest. ”&page&Because the king left his seat, it was not true that he was lying in bed.\nBut in the middle of the night, when everyone is asleep, the only person who was awake is sitting next to the children\'s room (baby bed).&page&The real queen took out the child from the cradle and breastfeed it in his arms.&page&Then he shook the cradle of the cradle and corrected the shape and laid down the child to the road./J4nro8) covered.&page&The real queen did not forget the young roe deer.She patted her back to the corner of the young roe deer.\nThen the real queen quietly went out of the door.&page&The next morning, the nanny asked the gate guard soldiers, \"Is there anyone who came to the palace at night?\"\nThe real queen came in many nights in this way, but she didn\'t