gold coins came out every day.&page&He collected a bunch of gold coins.\nAs a result, I thought about this.\n\'I\'m only at the house, but what\'s the use of these gold coins?I have to go out of the world. \'\nThen he said goodbye to his parents and went to the world with a backpack and gun.&page&Then one day, I traveled into the dense forest, and I went straight to the end.\nIn one of the windows of the castle, the old woman was standing with a beautiful lady and looking out.\nBut the old woman was a witch.&page&She told her.&page&“There is a phenomenal treasure in the body of those who are coming from the forest, we have to take it from him, I know, my beloved daughter, that\'s more suitable for us than that.He swallowed the heart of the bird.It is a treasure of a gold coin under the pillow every morning. ”&page&She told her how she could get it, and from now on what role she should play, and finally, she threatened her and said.\n“I don\'t do what I have done, know how to be big.”&page&The hunter who came close thought of the virgin.\n\'I\'ve been around countless times for a while, and now I go into this beautiful castle and take a break.\nBut the real reason was because I fell in love with this beautiful lady.&page&When he entered the house, the lady was glad to welcome you.\nIn the near future, the hunter really loved this young witch, her misery her thought, she wanted to see her only to see her, and she wanted to give her what she wanted.\nThen the old woman said.&page&“Now it\'s time to get the heart of the bird, so that you can\'t make a mistake.”\nThe old woman prepared to drink, and when she was ready, she poured it into the cup and handed it to the lady and told her to give it to the hunter.\nI did what the lady told me.\n“Self, sleep, drink.”&page&He didn\'t know how to hand a cup and drank the heart of the bird.\nThe lady secreted it and he swallowed him.Because the old woman did it like that.\nSince then, hunters have no longer find gold coins under their pillows.&page&Instead, the gold coin was found under the virgin of the virgin.Then the old woman came every morning and took it.\nBut the hunter was now in love with his lover, so I couldn\'t get anything other than my lady.\nAt that time, the old witch said.&page&“We had a bird\'s heart, but it wasn\'t yet taken from him.”\nThe lady answered.\n“You can\'t just give him to him, he\'s lost all his property.”\nThe old woman was angry.&page&“What kind of cloak is that cloak?I must hold it in my hand! ”\nThe old woman hit her cheeks several times and did not listen to her.\nSo the lady had to do what the old woman told me.&page&She looked at the country far from the window, as if she was wet in excellence.\nThe hunter asked.\n“Are you standing with such sad eyes?”&page&\"Oh, my own,\" she replied.“Beyond the horizon (jewelry) is a mountain, and there are gems.So I thought it was sad to think that I wanted to go, but who can go?Can you go to the birds, you can fly to it, but it\'s hard for humans. ”&page&\"That\'s just?\" The hunter said.“I will wash my sorrow and give me.”\nWhen he hugged her with her cloak, he wishes to say, \"Give me to the mountain of the pomegranate.\"&page&Everywhere, the room room was smiling and the jewels were shining.\nThey gathered only the most beautiful and valuable things together.\nAt that time, the old woman made her magic to make the hunter\'s eyelids heavy.\nHe told the virgin.&page&“We have some eyes here for a while.I can\'t stand because I\'m so tired now. ”\nAt that time they sat, and he fell into her knees and fell asleep deep.&page&While he was sleeping, the lady peeled off her cloak on his shoulder and wrapped her body and picked up the gross pleus and jewelry picked up.&page&However, hunters who knew nothing were awakened and saw that no one was there and recognized that his lover betrayed him.He left in a rough mountain alone.\nHe said.\n“Oh, I can do this in the world!”&page&He didn\'t know what to do, and he was sitting